data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This stunning property features four spacious bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, boasting updated roofing and air conditioning units. The kitchen and bathrooms have been tastefully remodeled to reflect modern aesthetics. With ceramic tiles and laminate flooring throughout, the home exudes both style and functionality.    Outside, a beautiful patio offers ample space on intricately laid pavers, surrounded by flourishing fruit trees. The property is fenced for added privacy and security. Additionally, a comprehensive water treatment system serves the entire house, ensuring quality water for all occupants.  Conveniently situated just minutes away from various amenities, this home offers unparalleled accessibility. Its proximity to the airport, Walmart, Publix, shopping centers, and restaurants ensures convenience for everyday needs. Moreover, it is a mere 30-minute drive from Walt Disney World via Highway 417 and less than 30 minutes from Universal Studios, making it an ideal location for entertainment enthusiasts.    For those seeking medical facilities and services, the home is also just minutes away from Medical City in Lake Nona, further enhancing its appeal and practicality for residents.
